'''诺尔·安東尼·克拉克'''（'''Noel Anthony Clarke'''，{{bd|1975年|12月6日}}）是一位[[英国|英国]][[英格兰|英格兰]][[伦敦|伦敦]][[演员|演员]]、[[导演|导演]]、[[编剧|编剧]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.entertainmentwise.com/news/43310/interview-noel-clarke-talks-adulthood|title=Noel Clarke Talks Adulthood|last=Luxford|first=James|date=2008-06-19|publisher=Entertainmentwise|accessdate=2008-10-23|archive-date=2015-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150106151324/http://www.entertainmentwise.com/news/43310/interview-noel-clarke-talks-adulthood|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/celebs/latest/2008/10/10/noel-clarke-answers-questions-on-his-film-adulthood-115875-20788738/|title=Noel Clarke answers questions on his film Adulthood|date=2008-10-10|publisher=[[每日镜报|Daily Mirror]]|accessdate=2008-10-23|archive-date=2020-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200611085542/https://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/noel-clarke-answers-questions-on-his-film-345933|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 生平 ==
1975年，克拉克出生于[[英国|英国]][[英格兰|英格兰]][[伦敦|伦敦]]，克拉克先是在[[北伦敦大学|北伦敦大学]]学习媒体，之后到伦敦演员中心学习表演课程。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article4147898.ece|title=Noel Clarke on Adulthood and avoiding trouble|last=Machell|first=Ben|date=2008-06-21|publisher=[[泰晤士报|The Times]]|accessdate=2008-10-23|archive-date=2011-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110616083313/http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article4147898.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2009年，克拉克赢得了[[英国电影和电视艺术学院|英国电影和电视艺术学院]]最佳新人奖。<ref>{{cite web | title=Film Winners in 2009 | work=bafta.org | publisher=[[英国电影和电视艺术学院|BAFTA]] | url=http://www.bafta.org/awards/film/film-nominations-in-2009,657,BA.html | accessdate=8 February 2009 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090117024112/http://www.bafta.org/awards/film/film-nominations-in-2009,657,BA.html | archivedate=2009-01-17 }}</ref>

